    "Description": "## Changes\r\n\r\n## 🚀 Features\r\n\r\n- feat: add azure devops support @olblak (#8586)\r\n- feat(autodiscovery/argocd): enhance support of ApplicationSet with multiple sources @af-beng (#8677)\r\n- feat: allow Updatecli manifest dependson @olblak (#8437)\r\n- feat: show updatecli warning if using outdated version @olblak (#8567)\r\n\r\n## 🐛 Bug Fixes\r\n\r\n- fix(autodiscovery/golang): correctly handle pseudo version @olblak (#8698)\r\n- fix(autodiscovery/flux): skip HelmRelease without chart template to avoid nil pointer panic @jouve (#8680)\r\n- fix: handle skipped condition dependencies in target gating @nickzerjeski (#8426)\r\n- feat(autodiscovery/precommit): detect rev version from comment @nickzerjeski (#8402)\r\n- fix(bitbucket): use FindBranch and paginate PR listing in pullrequest… @roulettedares (#8584)\r\n\r\n## 🧰 Maintenance\r\n\r\n- deps: Bump Golang version to 1.26.3 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8709)\r\n- chore(deps): update github.com/Masterminds/semver/v3 to v3.5.0 @olblak (#8699)\r\n- chore(deps): bump github.com/go-git/go-git/v5 from 5.18.0 to 5.19.0 in the go_modules group across 1 directory @[dependabot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/dependabot) (#8690)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/aws/aws-sdk-go-v2/service/ec2 to v1.299.1 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8671)\r\n- chore(ci): upgrade uv version @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8663)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/aws/aws-sdk-go-v2/config to v1.32.17 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8661)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/aws/aws-sdk-go-v2/credentials to v1.19.16 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8653)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/aws/smithy-go to v1.25.1 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8640)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/invopop/jsonschema to v0.14.0 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8623)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/aws/aws-sdk-go-v2/service/ec2 to v1.299.0 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8619)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/jferrl/go-githubauth to v1.6.0 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8615)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/fluxcd/source-controller/api to v1.8.3 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8610)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/fluxcd/helm-controller/api to v1.5.4 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8601)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/zclconf/go-cty to v1.18.1 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8558)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/drone/go-scm to v1.42.2 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8557)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/aws/aws-sdk-go-v2/service/ec2 to v1.297.1 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8552)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/aws/aws-sdk-go-v2/config to v1.32.16 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8544)\r\n- chore: update updatecli version and streamline workflow steps @olblak (#8534)\r\n- deps: bump Updatecli GH action @olblak (#8524)\r\n\r\n## 📝 Documentation\r\n\r\n- doc: add devoxx fr talk record @olblak (#8725)\r\n\r\n## Contributors\r\n\r\n@af-beng, @dependabot[bot], @jouve, @nickzerjeski, @olblak, @roulettedares, @updateclibot[bot], [dependabot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/dependabot), [updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) and updatecli\r\n\r\n## Sponsors\r\n\r\nIf Updatecli is useful to you, please consider sponsoring it.  \r\nYour support helps maintain and improve this project.\r\n\r\n[![GitHub stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/updatecli/updatecli?style=for-the-badge)](https://github.com/updatecli/updatecli/stargazers) [![Sponsor](https://img.shields.io/badge/Sponsor-%E2%9D%A4-pink?style=for-the-badge)](https://www.updatecli.io/support/#sponsor-or-donate)\r\n",
